'''Tenjin Shrine''' (天神社, Tenjinsha) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}} located in {{ill|Shiroi, Chiba|ja|白井市}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県}}, Japan. Under the {{ill|Modern shrine ranking system|ja|近代社格制度}}, it was classified as a **Village Shrine (村社)**.
