'''Tenjin Shrine''' (天神社, Tenjinsha) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社}} located in {{ill|Shiroi, Chiba|ja|白井市}}, {{ill|Chiba Prefecture|ja|千葉県}}, Japan. Under the {{ill|Modern shrine ranking system|ja|近代社格制度}}, it was classified as a **Village Shrine (村社)**.
== Overview == * Shrine Grounds ** Main Hall (本殿), Offering Hall (幣殿), Worship Hall (拝殿) ** Shrine Office (社務所) [[File:Tenjin Shrine (Shirai City, Chiba Prefecture) 02.jpg|thumb|Worship Hall]]
== Enshrined deity == * {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|菅原道真}}
== See Also == * {{ill|Inba District, Chiba|ja|印旛郡}} * {{ill|Shiroi, Chiba|ja|白井市}}
